     Cases_on `n <= m`
     >- (MATCH_MP_TAC le_trans \\
         Q.EXISTS_TAC `SIGMA f (count m) + SIGMA g (count m)` \\
         RW_TAC std_ss [] \\
         MATCH_MP_TAC le_radd_imp \\
         MATCH_MP_TAC EXTREAL_SUM_IMAGE_MONO_SET \\
         RW_TAC std_ss [FINITE_COUNT, SUBSET_DEF, IN_COUNT] \\
